{"tid":340822,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"電話想轉台 好煩惱！","createTime":"2017-07-30T09:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T11:18:26.000Z","uid":124811,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e53355f632e39b37ed1095a6a76c9e9dcf17a0d9","tid":340822,"uid":124811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"宜家用緊人仔<br />\n係好多年前老豆幫我上台嘅。<br />\n咁早排打電話上去同佢講想轉返我名，因為試過收錯我錢但一定要卡主本人先處理到，但家父老啦，又唔曉同個客戶服務溝通又唔方便同我出門市，好彩最後都搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果陣開始已經決定要轉返名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁岩果排就嚟完約，打電話去續約加轉名啦所以，點知電話條友叫我續咗先，遲啲再去門市搞。<br />\n點知去到門市又話要簽新約先有得轉名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就on9啦啱啱先簽完約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係唔想再用人仔啦又唔係快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問吓各位高人轉台有冇得攜號碼但用我個名？<br />\n第二，如果人仔提早完約要賠幾多？想盡快離開呢間廢公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7c48c1c456f853ce7c69b30d6d757da661f7a5","tid":340822,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:35:50.000Z","msg":"你都簽左約啦戇鳩 人叫你簽你就簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾中移都用到咁多年<br />\n捱埋佢 過多兩年先問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da57c3d1d85dee44f959d52e4b61d542c3f587f7","tid":340822,"uid":124811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都簽左約啦戇鳩 人叫你簽你就簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾中移都用到咁多年<br />\n捱埋佢 過多兩年先問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n簽唔係問題 但只係驚又再收多錢/有咩問題要卡主本人搞，好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無辦法嘅話當然照用埋佢啦會"},{"pid":"dbc97