ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時有得轉返名就得"},{"pid":"1b736d156bf1a23d0f241caf565af5c6e278b650","tid":340822,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"轉名都要續約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打去ofca投訴佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}